title: Government to force all drone owners to register, details expected Monday
text:
Government to force all drone owners to register, details expected Monday 
Published By: DigitalTrends.com - Today 
Drone buyers in the U.S. will soon be required to register their machines with the Department of Transportation, an NBC News report claims. ...
